<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: #f3f4f6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 30px;
      }
      .card {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px 25px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #0d263b;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2563eb;
        background: #f0f4ff;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: inline-block;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 6px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      }
      .expire {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #e11d48;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>{{subject}}</h2>

      <div class="code">{{code}}</div>

      <p class="expire">⚠️ Ushbu kod faqat 5 minut davomida amal qiladi.</p>
      <p>Agar siz bu amaliyotni boshlamagan bo‘lsangiz, ushbu xabarni e’tiborsiz qoldiring.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} Sizning Loyihangiz. Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
